bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989070/extras/4674f3c39bc9d1a93fb36bfc8c26b3d8.poster.avif?t=1745317904\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989070/extras/4674f3c39bc9d1a93fb36bfc8c26b3d8.webm?t=1745317904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989070/extras/e84f506231d980a5febc6106321f2b72.poster.avif?t=1745317904\" width=600 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989070/extras/e84f506231d980a5febc6106321f2b72.webm?t=1745317904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your citizens and send them on expeditions to learn more about the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration is an important vector of progression in the game. Explore increasingly remote regions to reveal new destinations, meet other survivors and convince them to join your city, find tablets bearing priceless knowledge, and bring back new plant species to introduce into your environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989070/extras/13a4af56d0a9043f775787ecbced12d1.poster.avif?t=1745317904\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1989070/extras/13a4af56d0a9043f775787ecbced12d1.webm?t=1745317904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_par